ActSoftwood Lumber Products Export Charge Act, 2006
SubjectExpiry of the Application of Section 12.1 of the Softwood Lumber Products Export Charge Act, 2006 Regulations
PrecisEXPIRY OF THE APPLICATION OF SECTION 12.1 OF THE SOFTWOOD LUMBER PRODUCTS EXPORT CHARGE ACT, 2006 REGULATIONS be made to set July 1, 2011 as the date on which to end the additional 10% export charge on softwood lumber products that originate from Quebec, Ontario, Manitoba and Saskatchewan.
